itinéraire découverte de la cité historique , office de tourisme de vence 2011   the town has a small chapel , up above the cité historique chapelle du rosaire ( 1948 , completed in 1951 ) , decorated with stained glass and other fittings by henri matisse , who owned a home in the village towards the end of his life .

french artists : from 1948 to 1951 , this fauvist designed & decorated the chapel of the rosary in vence , france

henri matisse